text.textblock: Radio Broadcasting Services; Kaukauna and Cleveland, WI

summary.textblock: This document dismisses petitions for reconsideration filed by WinCom Wisconsin Limited Partnership and Sheboygan County Broadcasting Co., Inc. See 56 FR 64210 (December 9, 1991). With this action, the proceeding is terminated.

supplem.textblock: This is a synopsis of the Commission's Memorandum Opinion and Order, MM Docket No. 89-486, adopted December 9, 1993, and released December 30, 1993. The full text of this Commission decision is available for inspection and copying during normal business hours in the Commission's Reference Center (room 239), 1919 M Street, NW., Washington, DC.
